319
00:17:41,404 --> 00:17:42,872
I'll play Sukwoo.

320
00:17:42,939 --> 00:17:45,742
-You can play Cha Moosik.
-Okay.

321
00:17:47,644 --> 00:17:50,847
"Moosik, can you lend me
just 100 million won? Please?"

322
00:17:50,914 --> 00:17:52,515
"Are you done already?"

323
00:17:57,220 --> 00:18:00,790
