343
00:19:18,969 --> 00:19:20,036
Oh, no.

344
00:19:21,605 --> 00:19:24,874
"Thanks for switching seats with me.
Take care."

345
00:19:24,941 --> 00:19:26,376
Oh, my gosh.

346
00:19:26,943 --> 00:19:30,547
"Thanks for a great year, Changseop.
