like a little Pocket Girl.

353
00:19:48,698 --> 00:19:50,100
Sorry, you're not a girl.

354
00:19:51,668 --> 00:19:53,837
I meant, P*k*mon.

355
00:19:53,904 --> 00:19:57,641
No, wait. Sorry, I meant Pocket Man.

356
00:20:03,747 --> 00:20:05,348
I can't believe I said P*k*mon.

357
00:20:08,151 --> 00:20:10,086
Sorry, I meant Pocket Man.

358
00:20:11,955 --> 00:20:14,891
I'm sorry, I used to be a Pocket Girl.

359
00:20:14,958 --> 00:20:17,694
