361
00:20:22,198 --> 00:20:23,333
You said "P*k*mon."

362
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:25,302
I'm so sorry.

363
00:20:25,368 --> 00:20:30,140
The siren went off,
but since I laughed while we were acting,

364
00:20:30,206 --> 00:20:32,208
-I'll let it slide.
-I'm sorry.

365
00:20:32,275 --> 00:20:38,848
You're so expressive that
