This is Chuu.

371
00:20:58,034 --> 00:20:59,869
Nice to meet you!

372
00:21:00,370 --> 00:21:03,373
-That was very cheerful.
-Yes.

373
00:21:03,440 --> 00:21:07,043
-I'll take this since you've used it.
-Wait, but earlier…

374
00:21:07,844 --> 00:21:13,216
Which emoji best represents Kim Jiwoo?
