I always send this emoji.

380
00:21:26,796 --> 00:21:33,503
So when they saw it was my most used one,
they said they weren't surprised.

381
00:21:33,570 --> 00:21:35,872
-This and--
-That emoji is so you.

382
00:21:35,939 --> 00:21:38,775
I'll probably think of you
when I see that now.

383
00:21:39,843 --> 00:21:41,344
Please give that to me.

384
00:21:44,447 --> 00:21:46,883
-But…
-Please let go. We have to move on.

385
00:21:50,654 --> 00:21:56,426
I heard you had a very special reason
for appearing on our show today.

386
00:21:59,963 --> 00:22:01,464
The Quiet Interview?

387
00:22:02,666 --> 00:22:04,167
How many questions are left?

388
00:22:04,234 --> 00:22:06,069
-Three.
-Three?

389
00:22:08,505 --> 00:22:09,639
The Quiet Interview?

390
00:22:10,373 --> 00:22:11,775
-Pick one.
-I guess this one.

391
00:22:11,841 --> 00:22:13,510
