-Please move closer to Chuu.
-Okay.

403
00:22:50,247 --> 00:22:51,948
-You stay. I'll move.
-Okay.

404
00:22:52,515 --> 00:22:53,950
-Okay, here we go.
-Sure.

405
00:22:57,053 --> 00:23:00,390
