-Really?

409
00:23:06,663 --> 00:23:08,632
-Go way back.
-His face isn't that big.

410
00:23:09,366 --> 00:23:10,634
-Keep going.
-How's this?

411
00:23:10,700 --> 00:23:12,502
Keep going until I tell you to stop.

412
00:23:14,604 --> 00:23:16,139
