419
00:23:34,624 --> 00:23:36,660
Okay. I guess there's nothing we can do.

420
00:23:37,661 --> 00:23:40,196
You can send a picture of yourself later.

421
00:23:40,263 --> 00:23:43,033
They can edit it in.
It's easy to do these days.

422
00:23:44,067 --> 00:23:48,905
